packets.name: PIXLcap - a PIXLwear baseball cap (Black/Red)
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: The first edition of the PIXLwear baseball cap, the PIXLcap. The cap is mostly black, with a red inner lining. Included are of course the PIXL logo and matching stripes at the sides and back. Designer: Pixls/0x303052. Manufactured with MagicaVoxel. PIXLwear (a PIXL brand) - ethical blockchain fashion from Austria.
